%% Diagram: tus 1.0.x resumable upload sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as tus Server

    Note over C,S: Phase 1 - create upload resource
    C->>S: POST /files\nTus-Resumable: 1.0.0\nUpload-Length: N
    S-->>C: 201 Created\nLocation: /files/abc

    Note over C,S: Phase 2 - query current offset (resume)
    C->>S: HEAD /files/abc\nTus-Resumable: 1.0.0
    S-->>C: 200 OK\nUpload-Offset: K\nUpload-Length: N

    Note over C,S: Phase 3 - append chunks
    loop while offset < N
        C->>S: PATCH /files/abc\napplication/offset+octet-stream\nUpload-Offset: K
        alt offset matches
            S-->>C: 204 No Content\nUpload-Offset: K + chunk
        else offset mismatch
            S-->>C: 409 Conflict
            C->>S: HEAD /files/abc (re-sync)
            S-->>C: 200 OK\nUpload-Offset: K'
        else checksum mismatch (extension)
            S-->>C: 460 Checksum Mismatch
            C->>C: re-send same chunk
        end
    end

    Note over C,S: Phase 4 - done
    S-->>C: 204 No Content\nUpload-Offset: N
